OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,FForcing the Irish education system's
OL,7,F"equality of opportunity" on Northern
OL,8,FIreland's middle class nationalists
OL,9,Fand unionists in a united Ireland
OL,10,Fwould be "very unpopular", an
OL,11,Feconomist has claimed.
OL,13,FJohn FitzGerald, adjunct professor at
OL,14,FTrinity College Dublin, has said
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland's educational system
OL,16,Fdoes not offer equality of opportunity
OL,17,Fto children from different
OL,18,Fbackgrounds, with "particularly
OL,19,Fdamaging effects" for working-class
OL,20,Fchildren.
