OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,FHe told the Joint Committee on the
OL,7,FImplementation of the Good Friday
OL,8,FAgreement that if Northern Ireland was
OL,9,Fto reform its education system, it
OL,10,Fwould reduce the cost of a unification.
OL,12,FProf FitzGerald published a report
OL,13,Flast month which estimated that the
OL,14,Freunification of Ireland would cost
OL,15,Faround 20 billion euro a year for two
OL,16,Fdecades.
OL,18,FThe findings were published by the
OL,19,FInstitute of International and
OL,20,FEuropean Affairs (IIEA).
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/14
