OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,FThe report took into account the
OL,7,Fcurrent level of funding Northern
OL,8,FIreland receives from the UK
OL,9,FGovernment, as well as the share of UK
OL,10,Fnational debt it presumed would carry
OL,11,Finto a united Ireland.
OL,13,FProf FitzGerald, who co-authored the
OL,14,Freport with Edgar Morgenroth, a
OL,15,Fprofessor of economics at DCU Business
OL,16,FSchool, spoke to the committee about
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland's educational system.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G3/14
OL,2,W+.!*% +!T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,Tppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
