OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F443A1714673301
OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,F"If you think about this huge problem
OL,7,Fwith the education system in Northern
OL,8,FIreland, we on this island, the ethos
OL,9,Fis one of equality of opportunity,
OL,10,Fwhether you're from a poor agriculture
OL,11,Fbackground or a working-class
OL,12,Fbackground, you should have an equal
OL,13,Fopportunity," Prof FitzGerald said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@MO]
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G4/14
