CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F443A1714673301
OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,F"If you unify and the educational
OL,7,Fsystem has not been reformed in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland, do you immediately
OL,9,Fforce the Irish system on Northern
OL,10,FIreland, which I know will be very
OL,11,Funpopular with middle class
OL,12,Fnationalists as well as unionists-
OL,13,Fbackground people.
OL,15,F"Or do you leave it there where
OL,16,Fthere's an ethos that doesn't believe
OL,17,Fin equality of opportunity, and
OL,18,Fdoesn't look after kids from
OL,19,Fdisadvantaged backgrounds in Northern
OL,20,FIreland?
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G5/14
OL,2,W+.!*% +!T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,Tppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
FL,444,442,8ff,8ff,8ff,8ff
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F443A1714673301
OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,F"You really need to do that and have
OL,7,Fthat in place before you unify because
OL,8,Ffor the Republic to say 'you're going
OL,9,Fto have to accept our ethos of
OL,10,Fequality of opportunity if you want to
OL,11,Fjoin us', that's going to be a
OL,12,Fdifficult sell.
OL,14,F"That's why I think it is vital that
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland reforms itself first."
OL,17,FProf FitzGerald also said he estimated
OL,18,Fthat to raise Northern Ireland welfare
OL,19,Frates and public sector pay rates to
OL,20,Fthe levels in Ireland, would cost
OL,21,Faround another 5% of national income.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUwD@gO]
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G6/14
OL,2,W+.!*% +!T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
