OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F443A1714673301
OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,F"Commentary on our report has quite
OL,7,Frightly highlighted the fact that the
OL,8,Fsubvention to the North is only one
OL,9,Felement of the major economic changes
OL,10,Fon this island that would result from
OL,11,Funification," he added.
OL,13,F"There would be a wide range of other
OL,14,Ffactors, some of them positive and
OL,15,Fmany of them negative. These have not
OL,16,Fyet been seriously examined."
