OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,FFine Gael TD Fergus O'Dowd asked if
OL,7,Fthey considered whether a significant
OL,8,Fcontribution to reunification would
OL,9,Fcome from the European Union, the UK
OL,10,For the US.
OL,12,FProf FitzGerald said: "It's very hard
OL,13,Fto see a large enough contribution
OL,14,Ffrom Europe to make a difference given
OL,15,Fthat Ireland will still be one of the
OL,16,Frichest countries in Europe.
OL,18,F"To expect the rest of Europe to
OL,19,Fsubsidise Ireland when we have chosen
OL,20,Fto unify is unlikely but it's possible.
OL,26,@tD@WOUzD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G8/14
