OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F443A1714673301
OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,F"In terms of the UK, they could be
OL,7,Fvery generous, but if they're very
OL,8,Fgenerous with Ireland, it has major
OL,9,Fimplications in terms of Scotland.
OL,11,F"We don't know for certain. We just
OL,12,Fthink it's unlikely."
OL,14,FProf Morgenroth said the cost of
OL,15,Freunification could end up being
OL,16,Fhigher, as the report did not include
OL,17,Fone-off costs such as changing road
OL,18,Fsigns.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUtD@UO]
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G9/14
