OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,F"Unification itself would lead to
OL,7,Fadditional costs and there are a huge
OL,8,Frange of them. Some of them probably
OL,9,Fquite minor, others probably quite
OL,10,Flarge," he added.
OL,12,F"They ultimately end up on the
OL,13,Fpractical side of things and we see
OL,14,Fthis currently with Brexit. There were
OL,15,Fcosts associated with Brexit that
OL,16,Fnobody anticipated and unification,
OL,17,Fbecause you're trying to unify two
OL,18,Fsystems, it's very, very similar only
OL,19,Fin the other direction."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@GO]tD@AOU{D@XO]
