OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,FHe also told the committee that the
OL,7,Freport "just talks about cost".
OL,9,F"We don't talk about the value of what
OL,10,Fmight arise and that's a really
OL,11,Fimportant thing," he added.
OL,13,F"Our paper and our work is trying to
OL,14,Fstimulate some discussions about how
OL,15,Fwe how unification could be done most
OL,16,Fefficiently and best for the people
OL,17,Frather than saying we should or
OL,18,Fshouldn't do it."
OL,20,FSinn Fein TD Rose Conway-Walsh was
OL,21,Fcritical of last month's report.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@^O]qD@AOUsD@QO]uD@AOUzD@QO]|D@
