OL,3,CHow education reform could cut cost of
OL,4,Cunited Ireland
OL,6,F"It was difficult to understand how
OL,7,Fsuch strong conclusions were given and
OL,8,Fexplicitly, considering the narrow
OL,9,Ffocus of the work that you have done,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,F"I think it's just important that you
OL,13,Fdon't have too many nuances.
OL,14,FObviously, you have to have certain
OL,15,Fassumptions in any paper, but the
OL,16,Fassumption just seems to go towards a
OL,17,Fheadline of 20 billion euro."
