OL,6,FProf FitzGerald also told Fianna
OL,7,FFail's Brendan Smith about the issues
OL,8,Fof students and graduates leaving
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland to study and work in
OL,10,FGreat Britain.
OL,12,F"Kids who leave school with A-levels
OL,13,Fgo to England, they don't come to the
OL,14,FRepublic to university, predominantly.
OL,15,FThey go to England, not Scotland and
OL,16,Ftwo-thirds of them don't come back,"
OL,17,FProf FitzGerald said.
